Uses of Package
org.transitime.core.dataCache

  • Packages that use org.transitime.core.dataCache 
    Package Description
    org.transitime.core.dataCache
    Contains server-side managers that keep track of real-time data such that it can be made available to clients via RMI.
    org.transitime.ipc.servers
    Contains the classes for the servers, such as the core prediction system, that provide data via RMI.
  • Classes in org.transitime.core.dataCache used by org.transitime.core.dataCache 
    Class and Description
    PredictionDataCache
    For storing and retrieving predictions by stop.
    VehicleDataCache
    For storing and retrieving Vehicle information that can be used by clients.
